Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:14.91,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どんな未来も　ふたりで見たかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:21.45,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どんな想いも　伝わる距離で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:28.17,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}君の旅立ち　覚悟してたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:34.34,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,750)\blur2}背中押す言葉　声にならない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:41.10,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,750)\blur2}最後につよく　抱きしめたあと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:46.65,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}ぬくもりと同じだけの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:54.57,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哀しみが　僕の心つつんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:01:00.70,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\blur2}優しくなるための　サヨナラ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:07.37,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}僕だけの幸せをくれたひと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:10.96,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつかまた会えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:15.76,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}本当の君が見つかるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:21.47,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑顔忘れないで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:14.91,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}無論何種未來 都想一同見證
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:21.45,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}有你伴我身畔 思緒才能傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:28.17,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}早已有所準備 你會踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:34.34,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,750)\blur2}幾欲衝口而出 終究未能表達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:41.10,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,750)\blur2}直至分別之際 深深擁抱過後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:46.65,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}與溫暖同等份量的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:54.57,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哀傷將我的心包覆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:01:00.70,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\blur2}為了變得溫柔 就此別過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:07.37,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}令我獨佔幸福的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:10.96,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}直至再會之日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:15.76,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}直至覓得真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:21.47,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}莫要忘記笑顏

Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的臉… 到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快點換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這身衣服是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算平時用不上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也要練習一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事自己做不了是很麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店… 店長？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊你好歹也是個店長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有些摸不著頭腦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明這麼年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會睡在哪裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺間 我就變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是個遲鈍的大笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方呆久了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憑什麼認為自己還能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要和非人之物扯上了關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就注定要成為祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連相應的覺悟都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就隨隨便便的答應
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是下場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認清現實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為喜歡的人把命丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是在超級初級的階段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒資格說我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡她？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能有多喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種突然冒出來的年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰… 絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你莫非是笨蛋丈夫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許對六花動粗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就站出來說話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以揍你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是這麼野蠻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才替人進棺材了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說在先
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這本畫書的作者是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想做什麼就做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快把身體還我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把六花還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼還不還的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長又不是我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她又不是物品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我才要拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點讓店長解脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答得這麼乾脆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再和我們夫婦扯上關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓店長成為你自私的犧牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也死一次試試
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能看清自己的輪廓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在世時完全想像不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睜睜的看著思緒無限的膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也去體會一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有身體的時候還有理性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你 現在也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:05:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只想著自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長會怎麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫婦之間的事只有夫婦知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今我不打算尋求你的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是求人的態度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 這個場景是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懸疑劇場？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做好去海裡潛水的準備了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不記得自己有招人仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你讓我越來越恨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:06:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡建起了一座高塔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然能一起看到那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要感謝葉月君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 島尾君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 六花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長這樣就好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者說 這就是答案？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來 我只是拼上命去被人甩？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終究還是被關進去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美麗而愚蠢的年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很適合悲劇收場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拇指公主這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在亂七八糟的畫裡做夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,景色和先前的都不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好一件意味深長的遺失物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個夢真不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不好的暗示？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不能在這裡不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心進了棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能也察覺不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我！ 振作點！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決不能比父母先走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是無聲無息的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是為代替那個自我中心的死鬼而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要為了我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後找到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓店長放心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扎扎實實的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在要打好基礎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我只顧哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正感動的時候 你這個人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有飯團吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我喜歡的餡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹹鰹魚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒哭一會兒笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天好忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花看上去比從前誠實了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從學生時代一起看過電影之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎就沒看過你哭泣的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚場的第三部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就說明這實在很稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來 我沒能讓她撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給 請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真不愧是我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願望化成了現實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想見她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個圓圓的頭就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可愛得很
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就喜歡乾鰹魚和金槍魚罐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種魚類製品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮭魚罐頭也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼原丈夫也在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如說有什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我… 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個眼鏡是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個頭是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我的夢裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會打扮得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在店長旁邊被叫「島尾君」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼整人遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 說你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我飄起來了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「啊」？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼反應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然在對面陷入假死狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候？ 三年前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能把身體借我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粘著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個氣氛是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得我的臉和店長氣氛不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻只感到火大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:13:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿背包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在… 我不想獨自被留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長在向我撒嬌？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易抓到你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…只能這樣認為
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是去尿個尿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 擺出那副表情說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為怪誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你比想像中要有精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你居然真的借我身體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如我們就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會下地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地獄？ 啊 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如這樣還…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用別人的身體為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算生前放棄得再多…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒有放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其留她一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如帶她一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這話說得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 我帶上六花一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:16:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你的身體被逮捕的時候接棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少開這種玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 給我遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長忘不了你也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算要持續一生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生離死別
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自然沒法看得很開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明知你不會回來 還小心翼翼的守護著店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背負著一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以… 不要再礙事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管離開了肉體 眼淚還…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:16:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為容器還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飯團…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒吃完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准用我的身體老想著吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君為什麼對六花這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反過來問問自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個愚蠢的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 六花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在等我回來吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後一個 我可以吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為最後的晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正合適
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 感覺自己變成了風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成了空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有實體的感覺好奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以這種狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不為人知的 做了三年跟蹤狂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎樣一番心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變態 抑或堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難以衡量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會把我看出洞來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是最後一次了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直留短髮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這圓圓的後腦勺 好美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個身體的主人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候變成了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事很重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在來這裡確認之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都以為你是葉月君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君的葬禮已經過去了三年以上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:20:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,途中葉月君進來打工
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多事情糾結在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能回答我的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店裡的禮物 那是島尾君？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起去海邊也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 一起留宿的 不是葉月君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留宿是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我不知道的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時對方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以為是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:20:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我喜歡上的葉月君…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？

Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:31.90,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,750)}いつも夢のなかでは　あなたは笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:39.12,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}どうして　ねえ　消えないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:43.21,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}I gave you everything. You gave me anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:46.88,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(750,500)}きっと　いつまででも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:49.80,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}You're everything, still my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:53.01,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}愛しているんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:22:05.44,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}真夏に降った雪のような　それは儚い奇跡なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:15.74,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}あなたに出会わなければ　こんなに切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:23.41,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}胸を締め付けることもなかった　それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:35.76,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}あなたに出会えなければ　強さも優しさも　知らずにいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:44.98,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}目を閉じれば　すぐそこに　あなたがいる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:31.90,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,750)}在夢中 你總帶著笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:39.12,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}為什麼 揮之不去？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:43.21,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}我給了你全部 你給了我何物？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:46.88,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(750,500)}我堅信 無論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:49.80,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}你是我的全部 仍是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:53.01,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}我都深愛著你
